INSERT INTO activity (
                    id,
                    title,
                    description,
                    activity_type,
                    distance,
                    moving_time,
                    elapsed_time,
                    total_elevation_gain,
                    sport_type,
                    average_heartrate,
                    max_heartrate,
                    start_date,
                    summary_polyline,
                    average_cadence,
                    kudos,
                    location_country,
                    location_state,
                    location_city,
                    athletes
                ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?,?)
                ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
